{
  "stem": "19982.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those things I do remember-- this especially in 1939, or maybe it was before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember it, like, in 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, 1939, summertime, they were talking already about the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And August-- we went away in July, but we are a very short time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father got in August-- like, in middle of August, he got caught to go-- again, mobilization.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he has to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- by September 15, he's supposed to be-- or 14-- I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in the middle of September, he's supposed to be in this and this place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, by-- completely by the end already, the last week of August, everybody was talking there will be a war and gonna be pressure of the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I really-- to me, the war was were they gonna fight there on the front.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was really worried about my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What-- they gonna take him to the army and that's what they-- this was, to me, war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then this was the last day in August, which is 1931.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A lot of people were going away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They was trying to-- to go further, closer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were going east, closer to the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then our neighbor, which is-- was our tenant and was a good friend, this Dr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Horne-- he was a very good friend of my father, even though they were completely assimilated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were not even as Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were more like Polacks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then my parents said-- they asked him he should take me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And most probably he said yes, because then my parents said, you-- you're gonna go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I still remember how I was crying and begging.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
